title: GUNGUNGUN v1.2
description: She probably shouldn't have stolen the guns and gold from those bandits. And getting that bounty put on her head doesn't help much either. The lawmen aren't too far behind the bandits. No way out of this one, might as well go out with a hell of a bang. A frantic and fast-paced 2D arena shooter with an eye for (gun) details. Earn a high score and increase the bounty on your head while fighting on a runaway train crawling with enemies. Featuring:- 8 Unique guns that mimic their real life
